msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce"
msgstr "Quiz rekomendacji produktów dla eCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce.php
msgid "https://revenuehunt.com/product-recommendation-quiz-woocommerce/"
msgstr "https://revenuehunt.com/product-recommendation-quiz-woocommerce/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce.php
msgid "Advise and delight your customers by engaging them with a personal shopper experience on your store, guiding your customers from start to cart and helping them find the products that best match their needs."
msgstr "Doradzaj klientom, angażując ich w zakupy w sklepie, prowadząc ich od początku do końca i pomagając znaleźć produkty, które najlepiej odpowiadają ich potrzebom."

