#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:67
msgid "WooCommerce"
msgstr "WooCommerce"

#. translators: %s: link to the WooCommerce plugin on wordpress.org (anchor text "WooCommerce").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:75
#, php-format
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires the WooCommerce plugin to be installed and active. You can download %s here. If you want this plugin developed for your eCommerce platform, please send us a message."
msgstr "Quiz rekomendacji produktów dla eCommerce wymaga zainstalowanej i włączonej wtyczki WooCommerce. Można pobrać %s tutaj. Jeśli chcesz, aby ta wtyczka została stworzona dla innej platformy eCommerce, wyślij nam wiadomość."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:95
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires your website to have a valid HTTPS/SSL certificate."
msgstr "Quiz rekomendacji produktów dla eCommerce wymaga, aby witryna posiadała ważny certyfikat HTTPS/SSL."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:109
msgid "This plugin does not work on local environments. It needs to be installed on a live website. Your website needs to be public and not hidden by a site under construction plugin because it needs connection to our server in order to work."
msgstr "Wtyczka nie działa w środowiskach lokalnych. Musi być zainstalowana w witrynie online. Witryna musi być publiczna i nie może być ukryta przez wtyczkę „witryny w budowie\", ponieważ wymaga połączenia z naszym serwerem, aby działać."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:124
msgid "Settings > Permalinks"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:127
msgid "Your current permalink structure is set to \"Plain\". For this plugin to authenticate correctly, a different permalink structure (such as \"Post name\") is required."
msgstr ""

